{"tid":1451173,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"機場文宣方向：共產黨危害全世界、香港係反共先鋒","createTime":"2019-08-11T18:28:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T00:37:52.000Z","uid":194177,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"bc0ab4c452f3cc71f0c747df1c6cf0630ebbe57e","tid":1451173,"uid":194177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:28:09.000Z","msg":"問心全世界發生咁多慘事<br />\n香港人都唔好話捐錢<br />\n睇多人地單新聞多幾眼都無啦<br />\n<br />\n作為旅客留喺你個地方幾日<br />\n仲要香港人成日西口西面<br />\n都唔洗旨意個遊客幾日時間會對香港產生咩感情而同情香港人<br />\n所以文宣方向一定要轉去輸出共產黨幾邪惡<br />\n點樣控制全世界意圖制造新秩序<br />\n令遊客知道中共最終都會燒到埋身<br />\n利用佢地對中共嘅恐懼作為支持我地嘅動力<br />\n受外媒訪問要講<br />\nHong Kong is the frontline battle against Communism.<br />\n而唔係淨係講D黑警幾暴力<br />\n無人care架！！！！<br />\n<br />\n我英文太廢<br />\n整唔到相關文宣<br />\n希望推到有人睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdbb761b31b1298ad6bab35b52a9c187ccf46ee4","tid":1451173,"uid":294635,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:29:34.000Z","msg":"唔好比機會共產黨有合理籍口出老解<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4aba56d89b0c214b98ab67782b47f159def65de6","tid":1451173,"uid":197492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:31:22.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"1400d47b20c117225656bd9f678c09539cd492db","tid":1451173,"uid":283109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:32:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">機場文宣整合post</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1450351\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1450351</a><br />\n<br />\n「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場"},{"pid":"41890b393b838c8eae40aba895de4a6cd256d814","tid":1451173,"uid":17081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:33:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8c4f75ba4ca047fe35bdf3cc30762b8819e3b00","tid":1451173,"uid":269515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T00:33:50.000Z","msg":"大家可唔可以整多少少人神共憤嘅俾遊客<br />\n好多時佢地知 Hong Kong fight for freedom<br />\n但好多時吸睛嘅係<span style=\"color: red;\">殘忍同無恥嘅行為</span><br />\n同埋可以出<span style=\"color: red;\">數字</span><br />\n吸引左佢地再講其他野<br />\n要令佢地覺得我地起人道災難入面<br />\n佢地係於心不忍 而唔係其他國家嘅野唔關佢地事<br />\n<br />\n文宣小妹有野想講<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1451498\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1451498</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"15c9f5e1b7dc7f927fda79de58893df9a77143db","tid":1451173,"uid":9583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T00:37:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CQB4x5w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCQB4x5w.jpg&h=df3c418f&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}